description: It has an easygoing nature. It doesnt care if it bumps its head on boats and boulders while swimming
abilityOne: DAMP:The Pokémon dampens its surroundings, preventing all Pokémon from using explosive moves such as Self-Destruct.
abilityTwo: WATER ABSORB:If hit by a Water-type move, the Pokémon has its HP restored instead of taking damage.
